    "141161885": {
      "title": "The Oxford handbook of attention",
      "abstract": "PART A: INTRODUCTION PART B: THEORETICAL MODELS OF ATTENTION PART C: SPATIAL ATTENTION PART D: NON-SPATIAL ATTENTION PART E: INTERACTIONS BETWEEN ATTENTION AND OTHER PSYCHOLOGICAL DOMAINS PART F: ATTENTION-RELATED DISORDERS PART G: COMPUTATIONAL MODELS PART H: CONCLUSIONS"
